1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,375
She had been mapping sounds no one remembered anymore.

2
00:00:03,375 --> 00:00:06,750
It arrived the way all forgotten things do — sideways.

3
00:00:06,750 --> 00:00:10,125
Every sound had a shape. She only needed to find where it lived.

4
00:00:10,125 --> 00:00:13,500
It had been ticking inside every silence, waiting to be named.

5
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:16,875
She drew one final line and heard, for the first time, the sound of something found.
